profile.bio: Neil is a member of the information security group at Twitter. He was formerly the CTO of Dasient, Inc. prior to its acquisition by Twitter. Before co-founding Dasient, Neil served in various roles at Google, Stanford Univ, DoCoMo, Yodlee, and Bellcore.
